article_title: Ice Cube dishes on his favorite Ice Cube movie
article_text: - Stars share their favorite Ice Cube movie on the red carpet at the BET Honors. The actor was honored, with music legends Aretha Franklin and Berry Gordy, at the awards show Saturday night at the Warner Theater in Washington, D.C. ()
